{
  "chapter": 5,
  "chapter_summary": "常剥皮（常无意）带着十万两银票和两坛女儿红，拜访隐居破屋的老婆婆。老婆婆见他是常漫天之子，态度骤变，显露武林前辈真面目。两人对饮间，老婆婆详述狼山势力格局：四大头目分别为老狼卜战、君子狼、柳金莲（柳大脚）和吃人肉的法师和尚，而真正的王是武功深不可测的朱五太爷。老婆婆赠常无意一枚有刀痕的铜钱，嘱其遇见左手七指的夜狼时交出，可救命。常无意随后向小马、蓝兰等人宣布上山规则：不碰女人、不能醒酒。众人登山途中，常无意以掌击毙香香坐骑以立规矩，小马当面嘲讽引发对峙。黄昏时分，三名狼人现身。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常剥皮",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "银票是十万两，酒是二十年陈的女儿红。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "晚辈姓常，叫常无意，在家里排第三。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你老子是常漫天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这是好酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "坐下来陪我饮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "喝酒要公平，我们一人一坛。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我喝一口，你喝一口。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "想不到你这孩子还有点意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "至少比你老子有意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 61,
      "line_end": 61
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你也想跟他们上狼山去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 63
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 67
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你老子已死了，你大哥、二哥也死了，你们家的人几乎死尽死绝。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 69,
      "line_end": 69
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 73
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你不想死？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 75,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 77
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我拿了你的钱，喝了你的酒，我也不想让你死。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 79,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "可是你上了狼山，我也不一定保证你能活着下来！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 87,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "狼山上有各式各样的狼，有日狼，有夜狼，有君子狼，有小人狼，有不吃人的狼，还有真吃人的狼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 89
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这些狼里面，你知不知道最可怕的是哪种狼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "君子狼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 95
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "看来你不但很有意思，而且很不笨。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "君子狼的老大，就叫做君子，这个人看来就象是个道学先生，不管做什么事都中规中矩，说话更斯文客气，不知道他的人，看见他一定会觉得他又可佩、又可亲。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 101,
      "line_end": 103
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "可是这个人简直就他妈的不是个人，简直该砍头三万七千八百六十次。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 107
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "除了这些狼之外，现在山上又多了一种狼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "哪种？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 115,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "他们叫嬉狼，又叫做迷狼。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "他们年纪都不大，大多都是山上狼人第二代，一生下来就命中注定了是个狼人，要在狼山上过一辈子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 123,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "他们对什么事都不在乎，吃得随便，穿得破烂，有时会无缘无故的杀人，有时又会救人。只要你不去惹他们，他们通常也不会惹你，所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "所以我最好不要去惹他们。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 143,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你最好装作看不见，就算他们脱光了在你面前翻跟斗，你最好也装作看不见。因为这群人里面，有很多都可算作年轻一代中的高手。尤其是老狼卜战的三个儿子，和狼君子的两个女儿。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 145,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "听说狼山上有四个大头目，卜战和君子狼就是其中两个？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "可是他们对自己的儿女却连一点法子都没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 157
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "除了卜战和君子狼外，还有两个头目是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "一个叫柳金莲，是头母狼。只可惜她的三寸金莲是横量的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 163
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "柳金莲就是柳大脚？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 165,
      "line_end": 165
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这头母狼又淫又凶，最恨别人叫她大脚，她若知道你杀她的老公，说不定会拿你来代替，那你就赶快死了算了！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "还有一个叫法师，是个和尚，不念经也不吃素的和尚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "他吃什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "只吃人肉——新鲜的人肉。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "据说他们四个还不算真的是狼山上的首脑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 187
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "嘱。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 189,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "真正的首脑是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你不必问。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "因为你看不到他的，连狼山上的人都很难看到他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "他从来不自己出手？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你最好不要希望他自己出手。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "因为他只要一出手，你就死定了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我知道你心里一定很不服气，我也知道你的武功很不错，可是跟朱五太爷比起来，你还差得太远。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "连我跟他比起来都差得远，否则我又何必在这里受苦？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "他不但是狼山上的王，只要他高兴，随便到什么地方都可以称王。当今江湖中的高手们，几乎已没有一个人的武功能比得上他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你为什么不问我跟朱五究竟是什么关系？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "因为我并不想知道。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "真的不想？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "别人的秘密，我为什么要知道？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你是个好孩子，我喜欢你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "这个给你，你一定有用的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "这有什么用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "它能救命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "救谁的命？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "救你们的命。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你若能遇见一个左手上长着七根手指的人，将这枚铜钱交给他，随便你要他做什么，他都会答应。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "这个人欠你的情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "只可惜你未必能遇见他，因为他是头夜狼，白天从不出现。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lao_po_po",
      "text": "我可以在晚上找他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你绝不能去找他，只能等着他来找你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_po_po",
      "speaker_name": "老婆婆",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "在别的狼人面前，甚至连提都不要提起这个人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "你们在里面说的话，我们在外面也听见了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "那位老婆婆究竟是什么人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "是个老婆婆。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我想她一定是位武林前辈，而且武功极高。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "这是你的女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "她若是你的女人，你就该叫她闭上嘴。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lan_lan",
      "speaker_name": "蓝兰",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "我若不是呢？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 313,
      "line_end": 313
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_lan_lan",
      "text": "我就会让你闭上嘴。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 315,
      "line_end": 315
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这次我们上山，不是去游山玩水，我们是去玩命，所以……",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 319,
      "line_end": 319
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "所以你还有条件。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 321,
      "line_end": 321
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不是条件，是规则，大家都遵守的规则。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 323,
      "line_end": 323
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从现在开始，男人不能碰女人，也不能醒酒。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 327,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若有人犯了这条规则，无论他是谁，我都会光剥他的皮。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 329,
      "line_end": 331
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "现在就歇下不嫌太早？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 343,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "现在已不算早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "可是现在天还没有黑。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 355,
      "line_end": 355
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "天黑了，我们反而要赶路了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 357,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "香香",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "为什么要在天黑的时候赶路？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": "char_xiang_xiang",
      "text": "因为天黑的时候比较容易找到掩护，而且这山上的夜狼们也远比别的狼容易对付些，何况……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "text": "她是你的女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你在笑？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "你在笑谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 379,
      "line_end": 379
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "笑你。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "speaker_name": "常无意",
      "listener": "char_xiao_ma",
      "text": "我很可笑？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "一个人若总喜欢做些可笑的事，无论他是谁，都很可笑。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "想不让天下雨，不让人拉屎，都是很可笑的事。想不让女孩子们说话也一样。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 391
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_ma",
      "speaker_name": "小马",
      "listener": "char_chang_wu_yi",
      "text": "听说驴皮也可卖点钱的，你为什么不去剥下它的皮？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 395,
      "line_end": 397
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_long_zi",
      "speaker_name": "张聋子",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "狼人来了。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 5,
      "line_start": 403,
      "line_end": 403
    }
